# 6. Project Structure

RevPay follows a structured project architecture based on **Spring Boot layered architecture**.

Main components include:

• Controllers – Handle HTTP requests
• Services – Implement business logic
• Repositories – Manage database operations
• Models – Represent application entities
• DTOs – Transfer data between layers
• Config – Security and application configurations

This modular design improves maintainability and allows easier feature expansion.

